data.description: This well maintained turnkey investment opportunity is a 9 bed, 5 bath home. Fully equipped kitchens feature all appliances, newer cabinets and low-maintenance flooring, paint has been freshened up inside and out, and roof replaced in 2018. Featuring over 3,600 square feet of living space main house has 2 bed/2 bath, full kitchen with stove & refrigerator, dining room, living room and laundry room. Downstairs has a 1 bedroom apt, separate entrance, full bath and kitchenette with eating area. Upstairs features private deck, kitchen w/ range & microwave, 2 baths and 6 individual rentable living spaces. You could live in one and lease the other spaces. Currentley multiple leases on the property.
